aye_wod_byrne-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/faye_wod_byrne-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/faye-webster">费耶·韦伯斯特</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-war-on-drugs">《毒品战争》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/david-byrne">大卫·伯恩</a>将出现在一个新的慈善汇编中，以帮助美国独立堕胎提供者受益。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="28" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-pearl-jam-and-more-react-as-supreme-court-overturns-roe-v-wade-3255372"><b>泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift)、珍珠酱乐队 (Pearl Jam) 等人对最高法院推翻罗伊诉韦德案作出反应</b></a></li></ul><p>&#39;现在的噪音，卷。 2&#39; 是同名非营利组织的最新发布，自<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taylor-swift-pearl-jam-and-more-react-as-supreme-court-overturns-roe-v-wade-3255372">美国最高法院于 2022 年推翻罗伊诉韦德案裁决</a>以来，该组织受到关注。</p><p>这张包含 11 首曲目的专辑还将有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/courtney-barnett">Courtney Barnett</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/devo">Devo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julia-jacklin">Julia Jacklin</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/big-freedia">Big Freedia</a>的贡献，并于 6 月 21 日发行，即上述法律修改后的两年后。 </p><figure id="attachment_3598629" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3598629" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3598629" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/Faye-Webster-Michael-Tyrone-Delaney.jpg" alt="菲·韦伯斯特" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/202